passive.name: Raging Waves
passive.description: Increases the wearer's CRIT Rate by <orangeStrong>{{1, percent}}%</orangeStrong>. After a CRIT Hit, there is a <orangeStrong>{{2, percent}}%</orangeStrong> fixed chance to dispel 1 buff on the target enemy. This effect can only trigger 1 time per attack.
